{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "以命換命", "storyInfo": "血魔大君燒毀了坎伯蘭公爵府，處決多名貴族。為了保護工廠其他人，凱瑟琳選擇直面薩卡茲雇傭兵。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "艾爾希，一定有東西不會變！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "比如說，等我長大，我會成為蒸汽騎士，像那位林奇先生一樣！不，我會比林奇先生還要厲害！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會保護你們，把壞人都趕走。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會像曾曾曾曾祖母一樣，讓坎伯蘭這個名字永遠閃耀。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "艾爾希，我保證，我會讓你看見的！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$burningloop1", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i03", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "y": 80.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 5.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.05, "yScaleTo": 1.05, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾爾希！！！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撐住，我，我馬上就......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過你的，我......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.5, "b": 0.1, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i03", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 0.82, "yScaleTo": 0.82, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，馬上離開。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血魔在靠近，你不能被發現。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾爾希還在這裡，我必須——", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你必須遵守她的命令，她不會允許你自作主張。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，你們不能......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們能。我們聽從公爵的命令來協助你“完成任務”，不是你的僕人。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘記她是怎麼教你的。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘記你的立場。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你必須做的只有一件事，那就是完成你的使命。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某一個瞬間，阿勒黛忘了自己在哪裡，身邊又站著誰。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她很想往前跑，很想衝進那場正在奪走她殘餘人生的大火裡。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像二十六年前的那個夜晚，她想要衝進另一片火光中，阻止議會的士兵帶走父親。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於其他的事，你早就沒有資格了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛睜大眼睛，她眼中的淚水被火焰烤乾了。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她確實無疑地看到，燃燒的花園中，正有一個巨大的身影拔地而起。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那具殘損的蒸汽甲胄嗎？是曾經凝集著她無數幻想與奢望的蒸汽甲胄嗎？"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到目標人物的身邊，馬上。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在無數艱難的時刻，阿勒黛用盡全身力氣祈禱，希望那位偉大的先祖會重新降臨到蒸汽甲胄之上，幫她渡過難關。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，她看到了，古老的鎧甲，正噴吐著最可怖的烈焰。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看見了火焰之中的陰影正對自己咆哮。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是她的希望，她早已漸行漸遠。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若祖先真的歸來——"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛知道，那只會是她的夢魘。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴她。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會一如既往，遵循她的意願。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不明白，大君閣下......", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為您對我們的招待十分滿意......", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您甚至會偶爾光顧我們的舞會，不是嗎？您是喜歡這裡的！", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不得不承認，你們一度給我帶來了一些快樂。", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#8$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們那些小心的諂媚，誇張的示好，都曾讓我心生憐愛。", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是不是弄錯了什麼？我跟大公爵與反抗軍絕無一絲一毫的牽扯！我保證......", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要真的有什麼問題，那也是那個姓坎伯蘭的女人做的！我可以向您檢舉她！", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人......閣下......什麼都好，您行行好吧，想要什麼我都可以給您！我的那些收藏品，我的錢，都請您拿去！只求您......", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，我要這些做什麼？", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不會殺了我的，對吧？我們還可以繼續舉辦那些酒會，您一定還沒有嘗過我珍藏的酒......", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托中校，我會沒事的，對吧，這裡是倫蒂尼姆！", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們，薩卡茲們只是受到卡文迪許公爵那個倒楣蛋邀請，來保護倫蒂尼姆的，他們從不濫殺無辜，對吧？", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶去前面。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太吵了。快些開始吧。", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開、開始什麼？", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等聽到命令，你就往裡面跑。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能順利跑進房子裡，確定裡面沒有活人的話，你就也能活著出來。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裡面......您是說火裡？您讓我跑進這麼大的火裡？不，我不會跑的，我不想被燒死！", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會照做的。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古老的薩卡茲站在維多利亞的心臟上，輕輕抬了抬手指。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔呃——！", "name": "市儈的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他沒有看清身後在追逐著他的是什麼。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像薩卡茲戰士說的那樣，他的確本能地遵守了指令，拼命往前跑去。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面是火，火裡至少還有一絲生機。正在追著他的才是絕對的死亡的氣息。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他的腳步還是太慌亂，沒跑幾步就跌倒了。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_blood", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鮮血自他身體內部迸發了出來。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stream_loop", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們不再屬於原本的主人，而是成了另一個人的僕從。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他的指揮下撲向面前的大地，撲向崩塌著的宅邸，撲向兇猛的大火，咬碎殘垣，吞下殘枝，蓋住灰燼。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血液在行軍，而且無人可擋，就連火焰都不行。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托，他說得對。", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒嘗過他珍藏的酒。", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們該去嘗嘗的，不是嗎？", "name": "血魔大君"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_410_1#7$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_054", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了，在這裡等著。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隆德，查理......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡就是你們打算處決我們的地方。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你怎麼知道的。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還不簡單。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩年下來，你們從來沒有讓工人們知道你們在造什麼。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們這些領頭的工人，卻也多多少少知道了一些什麼。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近催得這麼緊，恐怕是已經接近尾聲了吧，既然如此，我們這些知道太多的人，也就該死了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你剛才騙了我。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，只是處理了一點後事而已。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這些工人任勞任怨了三年，能掀起什麼風浪？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想給我耍花招。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來幾個人，跟我去外面看看。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明椒，給我看著她。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_054"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_054"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能抽煙嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......可以。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lighter", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smokefemale", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有想過逃跑嗎？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃跑？跑去哪裡？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我如果逃跑了，我工廠裡的那些工人就遭殃了，孩子。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#7$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在想，你們會怎麼對待我們，看起來，你們上面的人還挺有人情味。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣算是......有人情味嗎？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你們下命令的人應該說過，不要在工人裡掀起恐慌，所以才會把我們聚集在一起悄悄處理掉吧。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我的一條命，能換來更多工人繼續活下去，那就這樣吧。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為其他被你們帶來的老東西，心裡不明白嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，你今年幾歲？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你知道蒸汽騎士的故事嗎？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "知道。;聽過一些。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line227", "option2": "line227"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶曾經是打造蒸汽甲胄的工人。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對過去的我們來說，這是一種認可。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為守護這座倫蒂尼姆，守護我們家園的戰士，他們的甲胄是由我們的雙手打造出來的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經也憧憬著，有一天我能像奶奶那樣，能親眼看見那些偉大的事物誕生......能親身參與其中。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶經歷了很多事，她是看著倫蒂尼姆如何一步步走到現在的。我看得出來她很失望。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我......我還不想這麼快就放棄。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_box", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是這個抽屜吧......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗格，暗格......哦，找到了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是奶奶，一般人根本沒法發現這張桌子被改造過......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......我的工牌？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一本......筆記本？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我不知道我寫下這些能夠給誰看，又有什麼意義。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "哈威死的那年，費斯特還沒有出生。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "琳蒂試圖理解過他，但最終，她的思念都變成了對我的怨氣，她埋怨我沒有在那天攔住哈威。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我沒有辦法反駁她，我也沒有辦法責怪她最終拋下費斯特，離開了這個家。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "據說她改嫁了一個好人家，好事。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我沒有告訴過費斯特，我不想讓他知道，自己的父親死在了一場沒有帶來任何結果的抗議中，而他的母親，是帶著恨離開這個家的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你是在哥倫比亞長大的。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我是被我姥姥帶大的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的爸爸媽媽都是傭兵，不過他們都死了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼還要當傭兵？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我要養活我和姥姥呀。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多地方都不歡迎薩卡茲，我就只好也來當傭兵了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好孩子。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你也同意你們那個攝政王的做法嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指佔領這座城市嗎？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我不知道。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#13$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是收錢辦事，一開始，我都不知道，我們是要來佔領這麼大的一座城市的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哥倫比亞，我們的任務也就是替一些見不得光的商人押送一些貨物，或是獵殺野獸。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只記得，我頭一回見到格林那麼激動，是他跟我說，要是這次能成功，薩卡茲就能過上好日子了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格林？那個愛抽煙的格林嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他人呢，有陣子沒見到他了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他死了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你不難過嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格林告訴過我，對我們雇傭兵來說，生離死別是很正常的事。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生離死別。哪怕這座城市混亂了這麼些年，維多利亞人也一點都不懂薩卡茲啊。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接著，孩子。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳從煙盒裡掏出了一件小東西，拋給明椒。"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣東西小小的，軟軟的，是毛線織成的，顏色還很鮮豔。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......指套......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格林......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是你給那個上了年紀的雇傭兵織的吧？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他食指受過傷，會痛，但也戒不了煙。我見他把這玩意兒藏在煙盒裡。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概他也捨不得用，浪費了你的心意。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走的時候，把煙盒給了我，當作那幾個月的煙錢。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他從來沒跟我提過你，但第一眼見到你，我就明白過來，他心裡一直惦記著的孩子是誰。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......才不......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道他對這場戰爭怎麼看。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#9$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我知道，孩子，他不用說我就知道......你還不理解，戰爭是什麼。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g5_ordnancefactory_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我其實有預感，費斯特也會離開。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他和哈威太像了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "仗著自己那點小聰明，就覺得自己能夠解決眼前的所有問題。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "看著他，我就會想起哈威。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會分不清，我心中的失望究竟是源自抗爭看不到結果，還是哈威沒有認清貴族們的面貌。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或許兼而有之。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我還是讓費斯特走了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我知道我攔不住他。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，在我決定帶你回來之前，我想過許多要和奶奶說的話。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來以為自己已經有了覺悟，這麼長時間，我們經歷了足夠多。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我現在覺得，我還是欠她一句道歉。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你們是親人。;她並不需要你的道歉，不是嗎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line370", "option2": "line370"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 371, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳永遠都是板著臉的樣子，很多人都忘記了，她只是個失去了生活的普通人。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$rebel_intro", "key": "$rebel_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "薩卡茲們從來不讓工人接近工廠的某些區域，但他們無疑正在準備一項危險的武器。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "大公爵的掣肘理應讓他們無法獲得足夠的資源支撐到今天。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是，無論是交給工廠加工的資材，還是我能夠打聽到的他們的處境，都證明他們有一條屬於自己的補給線。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這些原本應該與我無關。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我能做的，只有保住工廠裡的這些人。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但是——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我還是把我不應該記下的東西記了下來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "或許，我內心深處在想著，如果費斯特有一天來尋求我的幫助的話，我能比當年眼睜睜地看著哈威離開，多做一點吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "工人無法靠近那些線索，但是，我太瞭解這片廠區了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "適合被當作補給線停靠站的只有以下幾個地點。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是這個，博士！奶奶在地圖上圈出了好幾個位置——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這些地點必定戒備森嚴。;希望另一邊能有所收獲。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line399", "option2": "line402"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line405"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我們要接近停靠站恐怕很困難。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line405"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，即使我們無法靠近，奶奶留下的這些資訊也足夠有幫助了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 406, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然想要和奶奶告別。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，就留到下次吧。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我們該回去了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和我一起的雇傭兵，有許多人其實都不清楚我們到底是來為什麼而戰的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是沒有地方去了。哪裡都不歡迎我們。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而薩卡茲的王說，我們可以有個歸處，可以被統治，可以找到未來。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和你們之中的一些人相處過，看得出來，他們有些甚至沒有參與過真正的戰鬥。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會戰鬥！", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你殺過人嗎，孩子？不是那種明確到可以不用有道德負擔的惡徒，而是......人。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是工人，你也沒有殺過，不要用這種過來人的口氣教訓我。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在倫蒂尼姆待了這麼久，應該聽說過蒸汽甲胄吧？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，好像是很厲害的兵器，但是很久沒有出現過了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，但那是兇器。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我曾親手打造了那一台又一台的兇器。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我並不為此感到羞愧，因為那些兵器被用來守護了我生活的土地。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，孩子，你知道你正在為了什麼東西而揮動手中的兇器嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4071_peper_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#15$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}